      "published_date": "2025-07-09T00:00:00.000Z",
      "text": "SUBJECT: CNP Transmission Cost Recovery Factor (TCRF) Approved Effective September 1, 2025\nNOTICE DATE: July 9, 2025\nNOTICE TYPE: Update\nSHORT DESCRIPTION: On Tuesday, July 08, 2025, the Public Utility Commission of Texas (PUCT) issued a \nNotice of Approval for the TCRF True-up filing under Docket No. 58178 with no changes from the \noriginal filing. \nINTENDED AUDIENCE: Competitive Retailers\nLONG DESCRIPTION: On Tuesday, July 08, 2025, the Public Utility Commission of Texas (PUCT) issued a \nNotice of Approval for the TCRF True-up filing under Docket No. 58178 with no changes from the \noriginal filing. This filing has an effective date of September 1, 2025, and a total revenue requirement of \n$844.6 million.\nADDITIONAL INFORMATION: A reminder notice will be provided to the Market when these rates go \ninto effect.\nCompetitive Retailer Relations \nCenterPoint Energy Houston Electric, LLC",
